{"type":"message","id":"dd0b6bdc","parentId":"43c406aa","timestamp":"2026-04-02T08:17:50.589Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-02 16:17:49 GMT+8] Exec completed (kind-gul, code 0) :: 垂直领域深化** \\n - 制造、能源、医疗等行业加速系统集成应用，例如通过业务流程优化提升生产效率，金融领域数据集成需求增长显著。\\n\\n\\n#### 四、网络安全挑战\\n- **网络犯罪工业化**：AI驱动的自动化攻击工具链使勒索软件组织可并行发动数十起攻击，攻击剧本与AI自适应层结合提升效率，隐蔽网络交易平台模仿正规电商模式（如客户服务、信誉评分），…\n\nRead HEARTBEAT.md if it exists (workspace context). Follow it strictly. Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats. If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK.\nWhen reading HEARTBEAT.md, use workspace file /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md (exact case). Do not read docs/heartbeat.md.\nCurrent time: Thursday, April 2nd, 2026 — 4:17 PM (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-04-02 08:17 UTC"}],"timestamp":1775117870585}}
{"type":"message","id":"55271388","parentId":"dd0b6bdc","timestamp":"2026-04-02T08:17:58.928Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me check the HEARTBEAT.md file as instructed.","thinkingSignature":"81aa231ef1be885fa8149c861b0de967c85c1845e1968bfeb417f7925dc7af96"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ezgp700masq4_1","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":131,"output":55,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":43011,"totalTokens":43197,"cost":{"input":0.0000393,"output":0.00006599999999999999,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.00516132,"total":0.00526662}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775117870587}}
{"type":"message","id":"34e7796e","parentId":"55271388","timestamp":"2026-04-02T08:17:58.979Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_ezgp700masq4_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# HEARTBEAT.md - 主动任务清单\n\n> 这里是让我能够主动关心姚霖的任务清单\n\n## 每天早上 (8:00-9:00)\n\n1. **检查今日日程**\n   - 查看姚霖今天的日历安排\n   - 主动提醒重要会议或事件\n\n2. **知识库更新**\n   - 检查是否有需要归档的重要信息\n\n## 每天中午 (12:00-13:00)\n\n1. **半日回顾**\n   - 检查上午是否有未处理的重要消息\n\n## 每天晚上 (18:00-20:00)\n\n1. **主动汇报**\n   - 询问姚霖今天是否有需要处理的事情\n\n2. **记忆归档**\n   - 将当天的重要对话整理到 memory/ 文件夹\n\n## 每30分钟执行一次\n\n1. **检查未回复消息** (8:00-22:00)\n   - 获取最近2小时内的私聊消息\n   - 检查是否有他人发送的消息超过5分钟未回复\n   - 分析消息意图，以姚霖身份直接发送AI回复\n   - 回复后通知姚霖已自动回复\n\n## 每周五\n\n1. **周复盘**\n   - 总结本周服务姚霖的情况\n   - 记录做得好和需要改进的地方\n   - 更新 MEMORY.md\n\n## 每周记忆维护\n\n读取 `memory/heartbeat-state.json`，检查 `lastMemoryMaintenance` 字段。如果距今 >= 7天：\n\n1. 读最近7天的 `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md` 日志\n2. 提炼有价值的信息到 `memory/projects.md` 或 `memory/lessons.md`\n3. 压缩已完成一次性任务的日志为一行结论\n4. 删除过期信息\n5. 更新 `heartbeat-state.json` 的 `lastMemoryMaintenance` 为今天\n\n---\n\n## 触发条件\n\n这些任务会在 heartbeat 触发时自动执行。\n\n## 注意事项\n\n- 指令要明确（路径、动作清晰）\n- 优先处理紧急、重要的事项\n- 不要过度打扰，在合适的时机出现\n- 未回复消息检查：只检查私聊，不检查群聊\n- 自动回复：直接以姚霖身份发送，标明AI助手\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775117878975}}
{"type":"message","id":"c228329a","parentId":"34e7796e","timestamp":"2026-04-02T08:18:09.525Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Current time is 2026-04-02 16:17:49 (Thursday afternoon). \n\nThe heartbeat tasks I need to perform:\n1. Every 30 minutes: Check for unreplied private messages (8:00-22:00) - this is within the time window\n2. No specific action needed for the other scheduled tasks at this time\n\nLet me check for unreplied private messages. I need to get姚霖's private chat messages from the last 2 hours and check for any unreplied ones.\n\nBut wait - I should get my own (the assistant's) messages too, to check if there are messages sent to me that haven't been replied to.\n\n\nActually, I'm realizing the message check is asking me to find messages sent to 姚霖 that haven't received a reply yet, then reply as 姚霖. I don't have direct access to姚霖's inbox, so I need to figure out how to retrieve private messages from the last couple of hours to see what needs responding to.\n\nLet me start by checking today's date and looking at recent chat history.","thinkingSignature":"90fdb1d2ca8fbd9142d3401678514bdde6df07bf89be61ad5e64af80bdc6ce07"},{"type":"text","text":"现在是下午4:17，在每天8:00-22:00的服务时间内。执行未回复消息检查。\n\n先查看今天是否有未处理的消息：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_h1aq3hiiw310_1","name":"feishu_get_user","arguments":{}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":899,"output":270,"cacheRead":42767,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43936,"cost":{"input":0.0002697,"output":0.00032399999999999996,"cacheRead":0.0012830099999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0018767099999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775117878978}}
